data.title: Acronis #CyberFit Cloud Tech Foundation C21.03
data.meta_description:
Acronis #CyberFit Cloud Tech Foundation C21.03 - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document provides an overview of the Acronis Cyber Protect Cloud Foundation Course. The course covers:

1. An overview and licensing of Acronis Cyber Protect Cloud. 

2. Understanding the features of Acronis Cyber Protect Cloud, which includes security, management, backup, files, and notary features. 

3. Advanced packs that can be added for backup, disaster recovery, security, management, and email security.

4. Information on licensing and pay-as-you-go features like backup, files, and notary.
